Lazio coach Stefano Pioli is told his players to keep their feet on the ground ahead of Sunday 's home game against Empoli .
The Biancoceleste are riding a seven-game winning streak in Serie A and won 1-0 at Napoli on Wednesday to reach their eighth Coppa Italia final .
Senad Lulic 's late goal gave Lazio a 2-1 aggregate win and set up a meeting with Juventus in the final .